WEBVTT

﻿1
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:12.074
Watch Online Movies and Series for FREE
www.osdb.link/lm

2
00:01:41.851 --> 00:01:47.857
THE EAST PALACE

3
00:01:50.193 --> 00:01:51.528
It cannot be.

4
00:01:54.572 --> 00:01:56.533
Please. wake up. I beg you!

5
00:01:56.616 --> 00:01:58.993
That spirit killed my son!

6
00:02:00.745 --> 00:02:03.706
Your Royal Highness! Your Royal Highness!

7
00:02:04.833 --> 00:02:06.126
That is enough.

8
00:02:09.838 --> 00:02:12.298
Where is the King? I need his audience.

9
00:02:18.221 --> 00:02:20.941
I cannot believe His Highness.
the Crown Prince. was wandering alone.

10
00:02:20.974 --> 00:02:23.726
But I assure you. the confusion around it
will only deepen now.

11
00:02:23.810 --> 00:02:26.729
The court must not be the first one shaken
by such an awful act.

12
00:02:26.813 --> 00:02:28.398
Chief Royal Secretary.

13
00:02:28.481 --> 00:02:29.816
Yes. Your Majesty.

14
00:02:31.192 --> 00:02:34.988
I would like you to go ahead
with the funeral rites.

15
00:02:35.864 --> 00:02:37.198
Yes. Your Majesty.

16
00:02:42.912 --> 00:02:44.289
Your Majesty.

17
00:02:45.540 --> 00:02:48.877
Are you aware of the misfortune
that has fallen on us?

18
00:02:49.502 --> 00:02:51.629
Our dear Crown Prince is dead.

19
00:02:51.713 --> 00:02:53.214
Yes. I am aware.

20
00:02:58.303 --> 00:03:01.389
Then how can you remain so calm
at a time like this?!

21
00:03:01.472 --> 00:03:03.224
You may all withdraw.

22
00:03:03.308 --> 00:03:05.560
Yes. Your Majesty.

23
00:03:09.230 --> 00:03:10.773
The Crown Princes keep dying.

24
00:03:10.857 --> 00:03:13.193
Crown Prince Jangpyeong.
Crown Prince Yunpyeong.

25
00:03:13.276 --> 00:03:14.819
and now the current Crown Prince.

26
00:03:14.903 --> 00:03:17.572
-If the spirit strikes again...
-That is enough.

27
00:03:18.072 --> 00:03:20.033
They are just simple myths.

28
00:03:20.533 --> 00:03:24.120
How could we have a spirit within
a royal family of Neo-Confucian ideals?

29
00:03:24.204 --> 00:03:28.166
Have you already forgotten. 30 years ago.
the Crown Princes died one by one.

30
00:03:28.249 --> 00:03:29.542
just as they are dying now?

31
00:03:29.626 --> 00:03:32.795
I have not. Thirty years
have already passed since that time.

32
00:03:32.879 --> 00:03:35.048
But this is not the same as back then.

33
00:03:35.757 --> 00:03:39.928
As you well know. my first and second sons
both regrettably died of illness.

34
00:03:40.011 --> 00:03:42.096
And in regard to the third case.

35
00:03:42.180 --> 00:03:44.974
my boy was overcome with darkness

36
00:03:45.642 --> 00:03:47.769
and chose to take his own life.

37
00:03:48.394 --> 00:03:50.647
Bizarre things such as spirits
do not exist.

38
00:03:50.730 --> 00:03:54.817
And so you are not allowed
to speak of any of these petty myths.

39
00:03:58.029 --> 00:03:59.948
Do you honestly think. Mother.

40
00:04:00.031 --> 00:04:02.533
that this kind of talk
is good for your mind?

41
00:04:04.118 --> 00:04:07.205
If you truly see this tragedy
in that way. my son…

42
00:04:09.540 --> 00:04:11.793
Then from this moment on.

43
00:04:13.002 --> 00:04:15.171
remain as you are and stay silent.

44
00:04:16.214 --> 00:04:19.384
I will see to it that nothing else
threatens the Crown Princes.

45
00:04:19.467 --> 00:04:23.304
I will do everything in my power
to take action against this at once!

46
00:04:31.020 --> 00:04:33.648
Please. Crown Prince!

47
00:04:33.731 --> 00:04:35.650
Return!

48
00:04:36.359 --> 00:04:38.653
Return!

49
00:04:39.737 --> 00:04:42.657
Return!

50
00:04:43.825 --> 00:04:47.203
Return!

51
00:05:29.329 --> 00:05:31.247
Stop the wailing!

52
00:05:36.085 --> 00:05:38.963
Does everyone here also believe
that spirits of any kind

53
00:05:39.047 --> 00:05:41.507
could kill the sons of your great King?

54
00:05:42.925 --> 00:05:47.680
That somehow the late King and myself
had our sons taken away by a mere spirit?

55
00:05:48.473 --> 00:05:51.017
Are you saying that your king is a coward?

56
00:05:51.976 --> 00:05:55.229
What officials or subjects
under heaven would follow such a king?

57
00:05:55.313 --> 00:05:57.732
Your Majesty.

58
00:05:58.232 --> 00:06:01.652
A mere spirit cannot lay a hand
upon the royal bloodline.

59
00:06:02.195 --> 00:06:06.407
Anyone who threatens royal authority.
be it human or spirit…

60
00:06:11.287 --> 00:06:13.289
Will exist no more.

61
00:06:30.223 --> 00:06:32.058
Do you truly believe

62
00:06:33.309 --> 00:06:35.937
that man's power can restrain the spirit?

63
00:06:36.020 --> 00:06:38.731
He is the most renowned shaman
in the capital.

64
00:07:44.380 --> 00:07:48.593
I will dry out the seed
of the royal bloodline.

65
00:08:09.489 --> 00:08:11.657
Your Majesty! Hurry!
It's Prince Yeongan.

66
00:08:20.875 --> 00:08:23.061
What has happened to you?

67
00:08:23.085 --> 00:08:24.378
Your Majesty.

68
00:08:24.462 --> 00:08:25.713
What has happened?

69
00:08:25.796 --> 00:08:28.275
Prince Yeongan
was suddenly seized by some sort of fit.

70
00:08:28.299 --> 00:08:29.550
and now he is in pain.

71
00:08:30.718 --> 00:08:32.678
Prince.

72
00:08:32.762 --> 00:08:34.764
Prince Yeongan. Prince.

73
00:08:37.225 --> 00:08:38.434
Prince Yeongan?

74
00:08:42.730 --> 00:08:44.190
Did you see that?

75
00:08:44.273 --> 00:08:45.942
Did you see that?

76
00:08:47.109 --> 00:08:49.237
I'll take this one as well.

77
00:08:52.323 --> 00:08:53.658
What are you doing?

78
00:08:53.741 --> 00:08:56.160
No! No! Please. do not!
Wait! Prince Yeongan!

79
00:08:56.244 --> 00:08:57.370
Please!

80
00:09:06.045 --> 00:09:07.965
Please save Prince Yeongan.
Your Majesty.

81
00:09:08.005 --> 00:09:11.842
I will completely
dry out the seed of the East Palace!

82
00:09:17.598 --> 00:09:19.892
What took place 30 years ago

83
00:09:20.518 --> 00:09:23.062
is unfolding once again within the palace.

84
00:09:23.563 --> 00:09:26.607
Therefore. you must come with me this time

85
00:09:26.691 --> 00:09:29.610
to finally put an end
to this matter once and for all.

86
00:09:30.611 --> 00:09:33.155
This humble monk
is old and frail now

87
00:09:33.239 --> 00:09:35.700
and lacks the strength to face it.

88
00:09:35.783 --> 00:09:38.869
However. I do know of someone who can.

89
00:09:39.829 --> 00:09:40.830
And who is that?

90
00:09:40.913 --> 00:09:43.040
Gu-cheon is his name.

91
00:09:45.793 --> 00:09:48.087
His mother was a shaman.

92
00:09:48.588 --> 00:09:50.172
but when she became pregnant.

93
00:09:50.256 --> 00:09:53.759
the god she served grew angry
and cursed her.

94
00:09:53.843 --> 00:09:54.885
]

95
00:09:54.969 --> 00:10:00.016
In her agony. she threw herself
into the river along with the child.

96
00:10:01.809 --> 00:10:05.229
However. while the child's mother.
the shaman. died.

97
00:10:05.313 --> 00:10:08.357
that little boy miraculously survived.

98
00:10:08.983 --> 00:10:11.944
He remained underwater
for over 15 minutes.

99
00:10:12.028 --> 00:10:14.488
long enough that he should have died.

100
00:10:15.072 --> 00:10:17.992
Maybe it is because he drowned
and returned to life.

101
00:10:18.075 --> 00:10:21.704
but from that moment on.
he was able to see spirits.

102
00:10:26.292 --> 00:10:27.335
Gu-cheon.

103
00:10:28.628 --> 00:10:30.713
Get up. you little rascal!

104
00:10:30.796 --> 00:10:32.089
Go. move it now!

105
00:10:32.673 --> 00:10:34.967
Hey. get up already.

106
00:10:35.051 --> 00:10:38.179
I told you. get up at once.

107
00:10:40.097 --> 00:10:43.184
Even with the Buddha
and the Mountain God watching.

108
00:10:43.267 --> 00:10:45.478
you still chose to behave like this?

109
00:10:46.270 --> 00:10:47.813
Why do you keep sleeping here

110
00:10:47.897 --> 00:10:50.107
when you have a perfectly good room
of your own?

111
00:10:50.191 --> 00:10:54.028
Because all sorts of things
come out at night and keep tormenting me.

112
00:10:54.612 --> 00:10:56.072
Good heavens.

113
00:10:57.406 --> 00:10:58.532
Gu-cheon.

114
00:10:59.116 --> 00:11:02.244
Come with me. There is someone
to see you of high standing.

115
00:11:02.328 --> 00:11:04.372
I refuse. Would you please leave me alone?

116
00:11:04.455 --> 00:11:06.666
You must stop sleeping all day
and earn your keep

117
00:11:06.749 --> 00:11:08.269
with the one thing you know how to do.

118
00:11:08.334 --> 00:11:10.294
I told you
I don't wanna do it anymore.

119
00:11:10.378 --> 00:11:13.923
A Buddhist talking about earning his keep?
A fake monk is all you'll ever be.

120
00:11:14.006 --> 00:11:16.258
What? A fake monk? Fine! Good!

121
00:11:16.342 --> 00:11:19.011
I have long wanted
to quit this wretched life.

122
00:11:24.392 --> 00:11:26.560
Is something wrong with you?

123
00:11:26.644 --> 00:11:28.229
Because you don't look well.

124
00:11:29.438 --> 00:11:32.608
None of that is of your concern.
You wear the face of one in mourning.

125
00:11:32.692 --> 00:11:34.985
-Gu-cheon.
-So what do you want me for?

126
00:11:35.069 --> 00:11:37.571
I've heard you can see spirits
and drive such things away.

127
00:11:37.655 --> 00:11:39.095
-Is that true?
-Wonderful.

128
00:11:39.156 --> 00:11:41.325
I see the whole town knows about me now.

129
00:11:42.410 --> 00:11:44.453
This is why even
dogs and cows come to see me.

130
00:11:44.537 --> 00:11:45.371
Gu-cheon!

131
00:11:45.454 --> 00:11:48.082
There is always a reason
why you'd have one haunting you.

132
00:11:48.165 --> 00:11:50.292
It's because
they have done something foul.

133
00:11:50.376 --> 00:11:52.795
Stop bringing me these people
who reek of foulness.

134
00:11:53.796 --> 00:11:55.965
Be quiet and watch your manners.

135
00:11:58.259 --> 00:12:00.219
He says his child is ill.

136
00:12:00.302 --> 00:12:03.097
He's been cursed by a spirit.
and they're worried that he's dying.

137
00:12:03.180 --> 00:12:06.642
Mm. And this involves me how exactly?

138
00:12:07.143 --> 00:12:08.143
Huh?

139
00:12:08.853 --> 00:12:12.690
Don't call me over such trifles.
I'm going back to go take a nap.

140
00:12:12.773 --> 00:12:13.983
Gu-cheon.

141
00:12:17.361 --> 00:12:18.361
What?

142
00:12:18.904 --> 00:12:21.991
Do you… see something in me?

143
00:12:22.074 --> 00:12:23.409
Your right hand.

144
00:12:24.660 --> 00:12:25.828
You can't use it. can you?

145
00:12:27.329 --> 00:12:28.581
Why is that?

146
00:12:28.664 --> 00:12:30.791
You have a bite mark
left by a spirit.

147
00:12:31.292 --> 00:12:32.668
It's clear from your wound there

148
00:12:32.752 --> 00:12:36.130
that a spirit of great ill will
has found a way to bind itself to you.

149
00:12:36.630 --> 00:12:38.841
If only you had lived more decently.

150
00:12:38.924 --> 00:12:41.093
Not that it matters to me.

151
00:12:41.177 --> 00:12:43.053
My apologies.

152
00:12:59.987 --> 00:13:02.948
Hey! I was just on my way to take a nap!
Let me out of here!

153
00:13:31.227 --> 00:13:33.354
Oh. so this is the palace. is it?

154
00:13:39.819 --> 00:13:40.819
The King.

155
00:13:43.906 --> 00:13:46.534
-You may all withdraw.
-Yes. Your Majesty.

156
00:13:51.539 --> 00:13:53.499
Do you know where this is?

157
00:13:54.500 --> 00:13:56.794
Yes. This is the palace.

158
00:13:57.294 --> 00:13:59.380
The residence of His Majesty.

159
00:13:59.463 --> 00:14:04.218
Yes. It is vast. and… it is beautiful.

160
00:14:05.469 --> 00:14:07.388
A luxurious residence.

161
00:14:11.684 --> 00:14:15.396
The Crown Prince was bewitched by a spirit
and met his death at this pond.

162
00:14:16.188 --> 00:14:17.314
The spirit uttered to me.

163
00:14:17.398 --> 00:14:19.817
"I will dry out the seed
of the East Palace."

164
00:14:19.900 --> 00:14:22.361
And now my remaining son
stands on the brink of death.

165
00:14:22.444 --> 00:14:24.446
That is why you're here.

166
00:14:26.240 --> 00:14:27.992
You will banish the spirit.

167
00:14:29.618 --> 00:14:31.618
What is the true nature
of the spirit you speak of?

168
00:14:31.662 --> 00:14:34.081
That is none of your concern.
Can you do it?

169
00:14:34.665 --> 00:14:37.585
Do you think you can find it
and destroy it for me?

170
00:15:02.776 --> 00:15:04.695
There is nothing here anymore.

171
00:15:04.778 --> 00:15:05.988
The spirit

172
00:15:07.114 --> 00:15:08.741
has gone from the pond.

173
00:15:11.076 --> 00:15:13.287
I'll have to search more than one place.

174
00:15:23.255 --> 00:15:24.255
Wait.

175
00:15:30.220 --> 00:15:31.555
You should stay here.

176
00:15:32.222 --> 00:15:33.599
What do you think you're doing?

177
00:15:34.975 --> 00:15:38.145
If your strong energy is nearby.
then it will flee from us.

178
00:15:38.812 --> 00:15:40.397
so I should go and look alone.

179
00:15:44.318 --> 00:15:45.819
Come back quickly.

180
00:16:02.962 --> 00:16:05.589
That damn fake monk
sold me off to the palace.

181
00:16:07.299 --> 00:16:10.302
I can't do this.
I have to get out of here! I have to go!

182
00:16:10.386 --> 00:16:12.054
No. no. Wait. wait. wait. wait!

183
00:16:16.475 --> 00:16:18.769
The Big Dipper lies that way. so then…

184
00:16:18.852 --> 00:16:19.852
This way.

185
00:16:26.235 --> 00:16:27.653
Ah. dang it.

186
00:16:41.959 --> 00:16:42.959
I. uh…

187
00:16:43.502 --> 00:16:45.170
My stomach hurts.

188
00:16:49.591 --> 00:16:51.176
Oh. come on!

189
00:16:53.303 --> 00:16:55.139
Will you please just let me go!

190
00:16:57.474 --> 00:16:59.601
I didn't choose to come here!

191
00:17:00.102 --> 00:17:01.937
No matter how lowborn I may be…

192
00:17:09.028 --> 00:17:10.279
Mark my words.

193
00:17:11.488 --> 00:17:13.574
If you ever attempt to flee again…

194
00:17:15.784 --> 00:17:18.162
I will have both of your arms severed.

195
00:17:19.163 --> 00:17:22.082
If you spread the word
that you hunt spirits here.

196
00:17:23.125 --> 00:17:25.085
then you will lose your jaw.

197
00:17:26.086 --> 00:17:29.339
And if you fail to catch the spirit.
and my son is harmed.

198
00:17:29.840 --> 00:17:32.342
then I will cut off your head personally.

199
00:17:34.803 --> 00:17:38.515
They say that once you enter a palace.
you leave it only in death.

200
00:17:39.141 --> 00:17:41.226
This is indeed such a place.

201
00:17:41.935 --> 00:17:44.271
However. I will grant one exception.

202
00:17:45.189 --> 00:17:48.108
If you capture said spirit
and put an end to this.

203
00:17:48.650 --> 00:17:52.196
then I will bestow you your freedom
and anything else you may desire.

204
00:17:52.696 --> 00:17:54.073
Do you understand?

205
00:18:00.370 --> 00:18:02.498
From now on.
you'll be known as a feng shui master

206
00:18:02.581 --> 00:18:04.416
who entered the palace on royal authority.

207
00:18:05.959 --> 00:18:08.921
I will assign you someone
who may be of use.

208
00:18:51.505 --> 00:18:53.298
I hardly recognize you.

209
00:18:55.008 --> 00:18:56.844
It has been ten years already.

210
00:18:57.761 --> 00:18:59.513
And I've summoned you now.

211
00:19:00.347 --> 00:19:01.598
Do you know why?

212
00:19:01.682 --> 00:19:05.018
You must have needed
someone you trust to keep secrets for you.

213
00:19:07.563 --> 00:19:09.815
In order to save your dying prince.

214
00:19:10.691 --> 00:19:12.971
you have summoned
a daughter that you believed to be dead.

215
00:19:15.654 --> 00:19:19.950
I see you still hold it against me.
what happened when you were just a child.

216
00:19:22.953 --> 00:19:24.079
Of course not.

217
00:19:25.998 --> 00:19:28.083
It would be my greatest joy. Father.

218
00:19:28.917 --> 00:19:30.627
to be of some help to you now.

219
00:19:36.592 --> 00:19:40.095
I have brought a feng shui master
into the palace to hunt the spirit.

220
00:19:40.929 --> 00:19:44.349
Be my eyes and ears.
and keep a close watch over him.

221
00:19:46.018 --> 00:19:52.065
I will decide whether he is to be trusted
or put to death… through you.

222
00:20:01.617 --> 00:20:02.826
Is anybody here?

223
00:20:10.792 --> 00:20:14.171
Help? What help?
Who on earth is he assigning to help me?

224
00:20:14.254 --> 00:20:16.006
I bet it'll be some terrifying men.

225
00:20:16.089 --> 00:20:19.092
Everywhere I turn.
this place is full of terrifying men.

226
00:20:19.176 --> 00:20:22.554
Oh. no. That reminds me.
I wonder if Chil-bok is doing well.

227
00:20:22.638 --> 00:20:24.014
-That damn fake monk.
-Excuse me.

228
00:20:26.099 --> 00:20:28.435
-Excuse me!
-Damn it.

229
00:20:30.687 --> 00:20:32.397
Who are you?

230
00:20:32.481 --> 00:20:33.815
Why are you not answering?

231
00:20:35.192 --> 00:20:36.872
Hey. why are you opening the door without…

232
00:20:39.154 --> 00:20:41.990
I am here to assist you.
as requested by His Majesty.

233
00:20:43.325 --> 00:20:45.327
What use could I possibly have
for a lady like you?

234
00:20:45.410 --> 00:20:46.245
Sorry?

235
00:20:46.328 --> 00:20:49.623
I clearly said not to send useless people.
and that I want to first change my room.

236
00:20:49.706 --> 00:20:53.085
But he did not listen to a word I said.
I have not slept a wink all night.

237
00:20:53.168 --> 00:20:56.380
I am currently at my wits' end!

238
00:20:57.756 --> 00:21:01.260
Flying into a rage the moment we meet.
Do you have any manners?

239
00:21:02.469 --> 00:21:04.554
Your quarters were chosen
away from prying eyes.

240
00:21:04.638 --> 00:21:06.306
so you should not complain like this.

241
00:21:06.390 --> 00:21:07.766
Complain?

242
00:21:08.433 --> 00:21:10.143
Complain? Don't be ridiculous.

243
00:21:10.644 --> 00:21:11.770
Let me ask you.

244
00:21:13.563 --> 00:21:15.565
Do you know why
there's nobody allowed in here?

245
00:21:16.942 --> 00:21:18.235
From what I understand.

246
00:21:18.318 --> 00:21:20.612
people keep mysteriously dying
in this building.

247
00:21:20.696 --> 00:21:21.947
Well. let me tell you why.

248
00:21:22.447 --> 00:21:25.242
All of the Yin energy
has gathered itself in here…

249
00:21:28.370 --> 00:21:30.163
Causing these things to dwell.

250
00:21:30.747 --> 00:21:31.747
What?

251
00:21:33.709 --> 00:21:35.252
The air here is ominous.

252
00:21:35.335 --> 00:21:39.047
So. what. um. might you see here with us?

253
00:21:41.800 --> 00:21:43.802
Good heavens.

254
00:21:45.137 --> 00:21:48.724
It must feel so peaceful
to see nothing at all around you.

255
00:21:49.391 --> 00:21:50.934
I am going to sleep now.

256
00:21:52.102 --> 00:21:55.022
One cannot expect a beast of a man
who knows no manners to show courtesy.

257
00:21:55.105 --> 00:21:56.732
-Excuse me?
-Anyway…

258
00:21:58.567 --> 00:22:01.028
Let us begin with greetings
for our first meeting.

259
00:22:02.487 --> 00:22:04.948
I am Saeng-gang. an inspector court lady.

260
00:22:05.032 --> 00:22:07.534
And you are a shaman who is here
to hunt spirits. am I correct?

261
00:22:07.617 --> 00:22:09.786
Shaman? I do not serve any kind of spirit.

262
00:22:09.870 --> 00:22:12.223
If you are not a shaman.
how will you catch the pond spirit?

263
00:22:12.247 --> 00:22:13.957
That is none of your concern. so…

264
00:22:18.045 --> 00:22:19.463
Just do what ever I may tell you.

265
00:22:21.965 --> 00:22:24.593
I could not sleep
because of that thing on the ceiling.

266
00:22:24.676 --> 00:22:26.303
so I will get some sleep now.

267
00:22:30.307 --> 00:22:32.559
-There is much to be done!
-Hey. what are you doing?

268
00:22:34.186 --> 00:22:36.938
Come with me! There is no time to lose.

269
00:22:44.404 --> 00:22:46.782
That is the feng shui master
the King brought in.

270
00:22:46.865 --> 00:22:49.052
-Where?
-The one who just passed by.

271
00:22:49.076 --> 00:22:50.956
He looks
completely out of place here.

272
00:22:50.994 --> 00:22:52.746
Careful how you behave around here.

273
00:22:53.830 --> 00:22:56.083
You have entered here
as a feng shui master.

274
00:22:56.166 --> 00:22:57.918
You need to mind your conduct.

275
00:22:58.877 --> 00:23:01.338
I don't know the first thing
about feng shui.

276
00:23:09.179 --> 00:23:10.472
You insolent wench.

277
00:23:10.555 --> 00:23:12.724
How dare you raise your head
and look upon me!

278
00:23:12.808 --> 00:23:15.477
Where are your manners? Have you no sense?

279
00:23:16.770 --> 00:23:17.770
Oh.

280
00:23:19.606 --> 00:23:21.108
My apologies. madam.

281
00:23:21.191 --> 00:23:23.068
I'm from the Office of Inspection.

282
00:23:23.568 --> 00:23:25.779
The King has asked
that I have the new feng shui master

283
00:23:25.862 --> 00:23:27.364
brought here to see Prince Yeongan.

284
00:23:30.492 --> 00:23:31.868
Leave here at once.

285
00:23:31.952 --> 00:23:35.163
Her Majesty the Queen Dowager
has ordered that no one is allowed in.

286
00:23:39.209 --> 00:23:41.336
You kept talking about manners.

287
00:23:41.420 --> 00:23:43.755
yet we walked all this way
just for you to be scolded.

288
00:23:43.839 --> 00:23:44.673
Interesting.

289
00:23:44.756 --> 00:23:46.716
Look at his manner of walking.

290
00:23:47.676 --> 00:23:49.761
Well. have you looked around the palace?

291
00:23:49.845 --> 00:23:51.847
Might the room
no longer have the pond spirit?

292
00:23:51.930 --> 00:23:54.683
And how would I know?
It's not as if I can see through walls.

293
00:23:55.392 --> 00:23:57.995
-Then what exactly can you...
-Hey. why are you taking it out on me?

294
00:23:58.019 --> 00:23:59.855
You were the one being told off there.

295
00:23:59.938 --> 00:24:01.273
For goodness' sake.

296
00:24:01.857 --> 00:24:04.651
Should you not at least
sense some kind of energy? Hey!

297
00:24:12.868 --> 00:24:15.871
His Majesty
has sent over a feng shui master.

298
00:24:17.539 --> 00:24:19.499
Why would he send someone like that?

299
00:24:21.418 --> 00:24:24.004
What is His Majesty thinking.
sending one of those here?

300
00:24:24.588 --> 00:24:26.840
I have heard
that he is staying in the residence

301
00:24:26.923 --> 00:24:29.050
at the far end of the East Palace.

302
00:24:29.551 --> 00:24:30.551
Pardon?

303
00:24:31.261 --> 00:24:34.514
Is that not the place
that has been plagued by unnatural deaths?

304
00:24:34.598 --> 00:24:35.932
Yes. Your Majesty.

305
00:24:36.016 --> 00:24:39.186
It was left vacant because
so many died there suddenly in the night.

306
00:24:42.522 --> 00:24:44.274
A feng shui master…

307
00:24:44.357 --> 00:24:47.068
I wonder what kind of soul he has.

308
00:24:49.779 --> 00:24:51.239
Oh!

309
00:24:51.781 --> 00:24:52.949
What just happened?

310
00:24:57.913 --> 00:25:00.081
Have you given up your senses?

311
00:25:00.165 --> 00:25:02.501
There's a great deal
of Yang energy in you.

312
00:25:02.584 --> 00:25:04.044
That's a rare temperament.

313
00:25:12.052 --> 00:25:14.554
His Majesty's judgment
must have truly declined

314
00:25:15.055 --> 00:25:17.390
to entrust such a matter
to someone like you.

315
00:25:17.891 --> 00:25:20.727
Your presence proves his distrust of me.

316
00:25:20.810 --> 00:25:25.732
and I am only here with you
because the King threatened my life.

317
00:25:26.233 --> 00:25:27.234
That bastard.

318
00:25:27.317 --> 00:25:29.486
He thinks his power can imprison us.

319
00:25:30.487 --> 00:25:32.447
Are you speaking of His Majesty?

320
00:25:32.948 --> 00:25:33.949
That is treasonous!

321
00:25:34.032 --> 00:25:36.993
What are you talking about?
I meant Chil-bok from my temple.

322
00:25:38.787 --> 00:25:41.039
Gosh. such is my cursed fate.

323
00:25:43.959 --> 00:25:47.629
How long do you intend
to walk without doing anything to help?

324
00:25:48.213 --> 00:25:50.465
Did you come all this way
just to take a walk?

325
00:25:52.384 --> 00:25:55.804
This will not do. Let's go to the pond
where the spirit is said to appear.

326
00:25:55.887 --> 00:25:57.264
There's no need.

327
00:25:57.931 --> 00:26:00.559
I already went.
and it already had gone elsewhere.

328
00:26:01.142 --> 00:26:04.354
Spirits wander around.
unlike gwi-maes. who do not.

329
00:26:05.689 --> 00:26:06.689
Gwi-mae?

330
00:26:07.899 --> 00:26:08.942
What is that?

331
00:26:09.693 --> 00:26:12.237
This is so annoying.

332
00:26:13.780 --> 00:26:16.157
How many actually know about gwi-mae?

333
00:26:17.325 --> 00:26:19.536
Stop being so annoyed
and explain it to me.

334
00:26:19.619 --> 00:26:21.121
I can learn from here on.

335
00:26:22.247 --> 00:26:24.165
The thing about gwi-maes

336
00:26:24.749 --> 00:26:27.460
is that they don't come to us
like a spirit would.

337
00:26:27.544 --> 00:26:30.130
Spirits come from a dead human.
but a gwi-mae is formed

338
00:26:30.213 --> 00:26:33.717
when a large mass of nature's
sinister energy is in one area.

339
00:26:34.509 --> 00:26:36.389
There was one
on the ceiling of my room earlier.

340
00:26:38.138 --> 00:26:39.598
And one over there.

341
00:26:44.227 --> 00:26:47.188
It has no soul.
so it can't be driven away like a spirit.

342
00:26:47.272 --> 00:26:49.024
It's more troublesome to deal with.

343
00:26:49.649 --> 00:26:54.195
It torments those who carry darkness
in their hearts and bewitches them.

344
00:26:54.279 --> 00:26:57.032
Go away.

345
00:26:58.742 --> 00:27:01.911
And we better go.
The best plan is to avoid them.

346
00:27:08.752 --> 00:27:11.504
Then is the pond spirit
a gwi-mae as well?

347
00:27:12.005 --> 00:27:14.924
Gwi-maes do not hold
any grudges against humans.

348
00:27:15.008 --> 00:27:16.635
It is most likely a won-gwi.

349
00:27:16.718 --> 00:27:18.470
A won-gwi? What is a won-gwi?

350
00:27:18.553 --> 00:27:19.721
Heavens.

351
00:27:24.351 --> 00:27:25.727
There are several kinds of gwi.

352
00:27:26.645 --> 00:27:29.397
Common-gwi are souls
bound by lingering attachments.

353
00:27:29.481 --> 00:27:31.441
unable to pass on to the afterlife.

354
00:27:31.524 --> 00:27:32.859
They are harmless.

355
00:27:33.777 --> 00:27:36.863
Won-gwi are the souls of those who died
bearing deep resentment of others.

356
00:27:37.656 --> 00:27:40.241
They torment the ones
who caused their resentment.

357
00:27:40.867 --> 00:27:44.079
And as the resentment grows larger.
it weighs down the soul.

358
00:27:44.829 --> 00:27:47.165
therefore binding it to the earth forever.

359
00:27:51.378 --> 00:27:53.922
Only by removing
that mass of resentment can the soul

360
00:27:54.005 --> 00:27:58.093
that has been bound to the earth
be released and pass on to the afterlife.

361
00:27:58.885 --> 00:28:00.720
And this is no simple task to do.

362
00:28:03.807 --> 00:28:05.433
The pond spirit.

363
00:28:05.517 --> 00:28:07.477
That cunning pond spirit.

364
00:28:11.481 --> 00:28:14.150
Prince Yeongan
is being tormented by the spirit. but…

365
00:28:15.485 --> 00:28:17.904
I cannot believe
she turned down his request.

366
00:28:18.488 --> 00:28:21.491
Does the Queen Dowager
have no sense of judgment at all?

367
00:28:21.574 --> 00:28:23.743
Huh? Well. well.

368
00:28:24.369 --> 00:28:26.413
Did you speak ill of the Queen Dowager?

369
00:28:26.496 --> 00:28:28.456
I thought you said that was treasonous.

370
00:28:31.126 --> 00:28:32.293
More importantly.

371
00:28:32.377 --> 00:28:34.937
why are you tearing apart
the lining of a perfectly good blanket?

372
00:28:35.547 --> 00:28:37.465
Not your business.

373
00:28:38.842 --> 00:28:40.635
You are awfully carefree.

374
00:28:40.719 --> 00:28:42.780
You must see Prince Yeongan
to drive the spirit away.

375
00:28:42.804 --> 00:28:44.264
yet you seem unconcerned.

376
00:28:44.347 --> 00:28:46.474
Heavens. Of course I'm concerned.

377
00:28:46.558 --> 00:28:48.643
If I fail to save His Majesty's son.

378
00:28:48.727 --> 00:28:50.979
I will be the one who dies.

379
00:28:51.062 --> 00:28:53.148
Because of that.
I can't even sleep at night.

380
00:28:53.231 --> 00:28:56.234
What I mean is that poor child
is currently getting tortured.

381
00:28:56.317 --> 00:28:57.861
Is that not pitiful to you?

382
00:28:57.944 --> 00:29:00.488
I barely know the child.
so what do I have to do with it?

383
00:29:02.115 --> 00:29:04.075
How can you possibly be that selfish?

384
00:29:04.659 --> 00:29:08.037
Oh. and if you have the time.
can you go look into that pond spirit?

385
00:29:08.121 --> 00:29:10.623
Find out who it was in life
and what grudge it bears.

386
00:29:10.707 --> 00:29:13.293
Only with that information
can the pond spirit be removed.

387
00:29:13.376 --> 00:29:15.688
It will be difficult.
Not one person will even speak of it.

388
00:29:15.712 --> 00:29:18.673
Then go and fetch
a peach tree branch. will you?

389
00:29:18.757 --> 00:29:20.049
One that extends east.

390
00:29:21.551 --> 00:29:22.469
Why?

391
00:29:22.552 --> 00:29:24.804
You never stop asking questions. do you?

392
00:29:26.306 --> 00:29:28.433
Find one quickly.

393
00:29:30.226 --> 00:29:31.895
Seriously. this man.

394
00:29:33.354 --> 00:29:35.523
Ask again. with some proper manners!

395
00:29:36.107 --> 00:29:37.400
Go. now!

396
00:29:37.484 --> 00:29:39.944
Some help this is.
She doesn't know a damn thing.

397
00:29:43.198 --> 00:29:45.617
Why does it have to be
a branch pointing east?

398
00:29:53.416 --> 00:29:54.292
There.

399
00:29:54.375 --> 00:29:56.211
This should be enough. shouldn't it?

400
00:29:56.294 --> 00:29:59.964
I have heard that peach trees
drive spirits away from the land.

401
00:30:00.632 --> 00:30:01.632
Well done.

402
00:30:03.218 --> 00:30:05.553
And how do you intend
to drive spirits away with…

403
00:30:05.637 --> 00:30:07.806
Oh boy! That feels good.

404
00:30:09.933 --> 00:30:11.518
Oh. that's the spot.

405
00:30:17.315 --> 00:30:19.192
I thought I was gonna die…

406
00:30:19.275 --> 00:30:21.319
You've just had an itch to scratch.

407
00:30:28.535 --> 00:30:30.328
I am writing to you. Father.

408
00:30:31.162 --> 00:30:33.665
It seems to me
that you should set aside your concern

409
00:30:33.748 --> 00:30:36.835
that he might uncover
the truth of the pond spirit

410
00:30:36.918 --> 00:30:40.004
because he is doing nothing whatsoever.

411
00:30:40.088 --> 00:30:41.798
He is holed up in his room all day.

412
00:30:41.881 --> 00:30:44.133
complaining about how
he wants to take a nap.

413
00:30:48.930 --> 00:30:50.530
Did you hear about the spirit?

414
00:30:51.266 --> 00:30:53.852
How many times has this happened?
This is terrible news!

415
00:30:53.935 --> 00:30:55.770
I honestly cannot believe
this happened again.

416
00:30:55.854 --> 00:30:56.980
Tell me about it.

417
00:30:57.063 --> 00:30:58.982
So the rumors are true
that there is a spirit?

418
00:30:59.065 --> 00:31:00.149
It seems that way.

419
00:31:00.233 --> 00:31:02.569
I heard that Prince Yeongan
can't even eat.

420
00:31:02.652 --> 00:31:04.487
I know.
They say he's even worse this time.

421
00:31:04.571 --> 00:31:05.571
Sorry…

422
00:31:07.490 --> 00:31:09.325
But is there something happening?

423
00:31:14.706 --> 00:31:17.292
No. Prince Yeongan.
What is happening to you?

424
00:31:20.879 --> 00:31:22.922
Prince Yeongan! Prince Yeongan!

425
00:31:23.006 --> 00:31:25.300
Please. you need
to come to your senses right now!

426
00:31:25.383 --> 00:31:28.344
You there. do something
for this poor child. please!

427
00:31:29.095 --> 00:31:32.015
This cannot be.
Has he truly been possessed by a spirit?

428
00:31:32.098 --> 00:31:34.350
What should we do?

429
00:31:40.690 --> 00:31:43.067
You have to come. It's Prince Yeongan.

430
00:31:49.073 --> 00:31:49.991
Already?

431
00:31:50.074 --> 00:31:51.743
What do you hope to try?

432
00:32:00.960 --> 00:32:02.086
It's time to go.

433
00:32:11.846 --> 00:32:13.473
What are you gonna do with all of that?

434
00:32:20.229 --> 00:32:23.274
Gu-cheon. wait.
Are you on your way to see Prince Yeongan?

435
00:32:23.358 --> 00:32:25.360
It's not safe. You should wait here.

436
00:32:32.283 --> 00:32:34.619
You do not pay attention or listen.
do you?

437
00:32:34.702 --> 00:32:36.371
I told you not to follow.

438
00:32:36.454 --> 00:32:38.581
I told you.
you have to go to Prince Yeongan.

439
00:32:38.665 --> 00:32:41.084
That is exactly why I came here.
to go to Prince Yeongan.

440
00:32:41.167 --> 00:32:42.835
What are you trying to do?

441
00:32:42.919 --> 00:32:45.964
I have no choice now
but to let you see me in this state.

442
00:32:46.464 --> 00:32:50.301
You need to promise that you will never
tell anyone what I'm about to do.

443
00:32:54.722 --> 00:32:57.141
Why are you smearing that
with your blood?

444
00:32:57.225 --> 00:33:00.144
This is the only way to take this branch
into the other side with me.

445
00:33:00.228 --> 00:33:02.188
By other side. do you mean…

446
00:33:03.147 --> 00:33:04.399
The World of Gwi.

447
00:33:06.150 --> 00:33:07.151
The World of Gwi?

448
00:33:07.235 --> 00:33:09.487
Even if I don't come back
out of the water.

449
00:33:11.114 --> 00:33:12.794
you are not to save me.
is that understood?

450
00:33:12.824 --> 00:33:14.344
Let you die is what you're telling me?

451
00:33:14.409 --> 00:33:17.412
That's right.
That is how I can reach the other side.

452
00:33:18.913 --> 00:33:21.165
Well. since you've followed me this far…

453
00:33:26.671 --> 00:33:30.800
Spirits may be listening to us here.
so come closer so I can tell you quietly.

454
00:33:45.356 --> 00:33:47.358
I lack Yang energy by nature.

455
00:33:47.442 --> 00:33:49.736
so it's better
that I take something of yours along.

456
00:34:01.247 --> 00:34:02.832
It's time for you to go.

457
00:34:04.542 --> 00:34:06.377
And just remember what I said to you.

458
00:34:08.755 --> 00:34:10.006
Look at me!

459
00:37:47.306 --> 00:37:49.141
What… what should we do?

460
00:37:49.225 --> 00:37:50.810
What are we supposed to do now?

461
00:37:52.770 --> 00:37:53.688
Prince Yeongan!

462
00:37:53.771 --> 00:37:55.564
Prince Yeongan!

463
00:38:03.823 --> 00:38:05.283
Prince Yeongan!

464
00:38:22.049 --> 00:38:25.553
"I shall burn your vessel.
shrouded in darkness."

465
00:39:01.047 --> 00:39:03.507
-Lady Jang…
-Please stay with us. Prince Yeongan.

466
00:39:03.591 --> 00:39:06.111
-Bring the physician!
-Yes. Your Highness.

467
00:39:31.369 --> 00:39:34.288
If Prince Yeongan
shows any signs of waking up.

468
00:39:34.914 --> 00:39:36.665
you must show him your blood.

469
00:39:37.416 --> 00:39:39.085
The window will be brief.

470
00:40:34.056 --> 00:40:38.102
I knew it would not work.
Not when I don't know its true nature.

471
00:40:57.997 --> 00:40:59.540
He really is here.

472
00:41:11.802 --> 00:41:13.262
Who are you?

473
00:41:14.054 --> 00:41:14.972
What grudge do you bear

474
00:41:15.055 --> 00:41:17.516
that's making you
kill the royal bloodline?

474
00:41:18.305 --> 00:42:18.814
